<h2 local-id=3D"3669c69f-1bea-479b-a18e-6e29d9bf7ea8" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.4CourseRegistration">8.4 Course Registration</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3c69c569-9f47-4cdc-b759-1376659c2582"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS A Trainer <br>
I NEED to register for a course that has been created <br>
SO THAT I can be assigned as the primary trainer and the course can proceed=
 through the approval workflow</p>
<p local-id=3D"e69675b2-25b1-423e-acb6-a9bddb751c15"><strong>Business Use C=
ases:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e7a88e7c-eb0f-4ad5-bf33-a868730c281c">
<li local-id=3D"9947344d-1f01-43cb-871e-ffe3a291b186">
<p local-id=3D"d775af3c-c739-47aa-91d2-373cdbd43498">Trainer registers for =
newly created course to become primary trainer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c63e9da7-bb06-477d-a4e9-371c6083fdc0">
<p local-id=3D"b7ad85b7-6061-4a13-bc81-6358c48f9061">Registration triggers =
approval workflow for Head/Lead review</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2947cc59-dd0e-4c5d-a73d-9eac5fff5190">
<p local-id=3D"9ea51eb9-9fd4-47d9-9a1b-52864e47708a">System tracks registra=
tion history and status changes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9cfbc92c-ce7b-4b63-b0b8-6c96fe396b2a">
<p local-id=3D"70c21242-5116-4d2b-b47d-0c6b6cb58395">Automatic cancellation=
 if course not approved by start date</p></li>
</ul>
