<h3 local-id=3D"001cbd94-3728-4f5a-bc9a-7d2e2197bec7" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.4.2RegistrationApprovalWorkflow">8.4.2 Registration Approval Workflow</h3>
<p local-id=3D"aef35c2e-a29b-48bb-b724-7deb27d2485d"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS A Head Channel or Lead Region <br>
I NEED to approve or reject course registration requests <br>
SO THAT I can control which courses proceed and ensure proper resource allo=
cation</p>
<p local-id=3D"9629f49d-6409-49e4-97f8-66a6e3aa2a56"><strong>Approval Autho=
rization:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
