<p local-id=3D"a3e51315-5ff6-4856-9039-1fb720e9877a"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6f6ee0e2-83be-4954-9431-ff99cc97ec4a">
<li local-id=3D"8680681c-e5c7-4670-b0f5-96f6955ca597">
<p local-id=3D"3d1e6ae7-b490-4af3-b8d3-3ec0fdbd5a8b"><strong>Approval Scope=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"c4f7bd97-b027-4a1e-ac72-778c2611a514">
<li local-id=3D"a35fc164-ac2c-4aab-8090-30f7a8e6beb7">
<p local-id=3D"8827c73b-961e-4b44-8b99-bfe735a59d2e">Head Channel can appro=
ve any course in their channel (all regions)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc382dac-7b4e-4033-8871-30cc70d6e987">
<p local-id=3D"6cae6c2e-4996-4599-b4fb-d955fd0831c1">Lead Region can only a=
pprove courses in their channel AND region</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29a5fb08-1ddc-46d9-86a0-53644bb3b467">
<p local-id=3D"a06bef8b-911c-4d2b-8c36-4a224c0bd8ce">Master Role can approv=
e any course (no restrictions)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"44b43bcd-daef-44bf-96fc-c174fb142935">
<p local-id=3D"558da6f5-66b9-46a7-8576-9de7345ac800"><strong>Rejection Reas=
on Mandatory:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"04abaeca-955c-4aa3-ae60-950bf8eebd8d">
<li local-id=3D"3418232f-5611-4d60-a1ff-6e8b3e84e1e5">
<p local-id=3D"b1d49adb-d777-42e0-8af9-b10c656bef53">Rejection reason must =
be provided (cannot be empty)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"09f0a6c3-b4bd-487d-824b-01c3bd9c179f">
<p local-id=3D"9ccada96-d333-4eb1-bbb9-4f6cb90e2823">Minimum length: 10 cha=
racters</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"240b180a-5370-4bb9-9291-dc2462ae3582">
<p local-id=3D"9a4810d6-e46f-4850-af12-ba8f3fdc6c6e">Maximum length: 500 ch=
aracters</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bba246cc-1fda-4193-a5e8-2c1400a2344f">
<p local-id=3D"765811f2-79b0-4a5a-9055-5f083a258ac8">Reason is stored in Co=
urse History for audit trail</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e47b94f8-9eed-4d05-b102-4c6555c528ba">
<p local-id=3D"e1654d02-3d3f-4f22-8ec4-1ac7636bfaff"><strong>Status Transit=
ion:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0e61456e-0ade-41f2-9755-aff176c07bcf">
<li local-id=3D"3c95379f-ae10-4c52-8c9a-212517d58ca0">
<p local-id=3D"081aeffa-379a-48e8-8a2e-968bb7840b43">Approval: REGISTERED =
=E2=86=92 APPROVED (one-way, cannot undo)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c0b6f3a-6838-451c-997a-a10fb30c3523">
<p local-id=3D"af80af51-de7d-43d9-bd37-992f0c269a1b">Rejection: REGISTERED =
=E2=86=92 NEW (allows re-registration)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba5217d3-f623-4392-82e8-b150ead2888b">
<p local-id=3D"e892b691-f276-4493-82d1-b51bc3446667"><strong>Trainer Assign=
ment:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4036b75f-32da-4b49-8014-4c2bf12ea956">
<li local-id=3D"a71eb8f3-233d-4c41-83ea-d94f9eff113b">
<p local-id=3D"32881eff-cdb5-4d88-8625-b12b94bd8117">On approval: Primary t=
rainer remains assigned</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b22477ba-8514-4280-beeb-2eab1758c1b6">
<p local-id=3D"4c1e1a7b-52cf-4119-b50e-2427c0a6ad9b">On rejection: Primary =
trainer assignment is cleared (course returns to unassigned state)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"7249bf51-1f17-4225-bb06-e3932d46b567">
<p local-id=3D"6c3455f0-032f-48dd-bf48-10d37d527163"><strong>Notification T=
iming:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d510aad8-0b2c-4c95-891f-528c2d450350">
<li local-id=3D"6a645f50-6524-4da5-8c77-c35bd0786438">
<p local-id=3D"686317c2-3d63-4ad2-9b0c-ced8514de765">Notifications sent imm=
ediately after approval/rejection</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d2a108b-c2a0-4fcd-b8b1-cd72e8c9aa84">
<p local-id=3D"2c131e79-8ac5-47b2-a17b-c7296b27d051">Email delivery handled=
 asynchronously (doesn't block UI)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0c8b9c5-6aa6-4dbe-a796-19a39162dda3">
<p local-id=3D"89e783f4-f425-44ae-a3a7-fb412e39bb53"><strong>Audit Trail:</=
strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3fffb94a-1708-4821-a42e-f8c00a3bd004">
<li local-id=3D"e93af094-7c09-494f-b98f-180ebf33048e">
<p local-id=3D"a8d7228b-6f53-4fa2-8905-64eca1677fd5">All approval/rejection=
 actions recorded in Course History</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77db4f51-61db-4134-9e63-edcec80a9403">
<p local-id=3D"c09b1a45-185e-47bb-b100-a22e712af8c9">Includes: User, Role, =
Timestamp, Reason (for rejection)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"51146754-4713-45e6-ac75-9f9c6479a593">
<p local-id=3D"1e66a200-8148-46ed-874f-83b2fd9d78cb">Cannot be deleted or m=
odified</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"d03b4d84-74da-4bfa-bcce-f062fe1d961b" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.4.3Auto-CancellationRule">8.4.3 Auto-Cancellation Rule</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7a564d61-00ff-448d-9247-97efeb3fc5d6"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS THE System <br>
I NEED to automatically cancel courses that are not approved by their start=
 date <br>
SO THAT resources are not allocated to courses that will not run</p>
<p local-id=3D"118da52d-c9c3-49f1-9dcf-c09cf3d00817"><strong>Business Rule:=
</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"fccda006-6ba3-4f58-aa6d-382dddb71779">Courses that are not a=
pproved by their start date are automatically cancelled to prevent resource=
 conflicts and ensure proper planning.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b50a6fd2-f0ca-47fc-a27a-49056ab10970"><strong>Auto-Cancellat=
ion Conditions:</strong></p>
