<p local-id=3D"731bd272-ba74-477d-8ca2-da381ee6bbe3"><strong>Auto-Cancellat=
ion Logic:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">IF (Cur=
rent Date &gt;=3D Course Start Date) AND (Course Status !=3D APPROVED)
THEN
    Status =3D CANCEL
    Cancellation Reason =3D "Auto-cancelled: Not approved by course start d=
ate"
    Cancelled By =3D "System"
    Cancelled Date =3D Current timestamp
END IF</pre>
</div>
</div>
