<p local-id=3D"6d3fdba8-187d-4442-be66-3bf0138ea5e0"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"df2d74b5-141b-4efb-889e-0e96c7b15302">
<li local-id=3D"31eab388-4e66-4534-9d05-11a591363b53">
<p local-id=3D"11f24112-db12-4d7d-b16d-b4d7aba14d9a"><strong>No Manual Over=
ride:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"fe022a3a-31c1-4a5e-bc3b-de4283444307">
<li local-id=3D"1f1359dd-0c4b-4d95-a2fb-f9de21b8ad26">
<p local-id=3D"b9c570d6-b33b-4f6e-b1b7-6a8a411c0de4">Auto-cancellation cann=
ot be prevented once start date is reached</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"425505bc-0951-410c-a0d3-3f875ee78cab">
<p local-id=3D"63d62295-99ac-40c8-b3d8-5ef748b8527d">Courses must be approv=
ed BEFORE start date to avoid cancellation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2da5288-be9e-4034-a4fd-6c6c95a8b472">
<p local-id=3D"0a1e663a-2257-4670-bbc8-a0c81f8b1ad9">No "grace period" - ca=
ncellation occurs on start date</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"49f25da5-568b-4f6b-a706-fa0f076b2fa6">
<p local-id=3D"271d1cbd-ff45-4e79-8283-59f508272a0b"><strong>Irreversible A=
ction:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"65887228-3af6-4eea-a513-ea3972386835">
<li local-id=3D"f98b8909-2770-4872-8b95-0c31ae8693ac">
<p local-id=3D"bd7a29aa-7f4c-46a8-8e29-df7633daf1ba">Once auto-cancelled, c=
ourse cannot be re-activated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e076b46-8430-4a12-b1c5-fe851de5ded7">
<p local-id=3D"17dcf9af-67a9-4704-ba9f-2b1cc0958ac7">New course must be cre=
ated if training is still needed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2d618cc-1588-49bd-b463-646ea3fe3055">
<p local-id=3D"8cd2c6d8-0ca5-4c74-99dc-28a70553e0a7">Course history retains=
 all records for audit purposes</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7c96453-13c6-40e4-8c09-e31c32747a3f">
<p local-id=3D"5cd8410d-642c-4c34-99da-5d4fb8b9978c"><strong>Notification T=
iming:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"27c4e934-aeef-48ce-a0ab-3e7686b047e3">
<li local-id=3D"954c33f5-2ae0-4eb2-a76e-b4fdabf02e2b">
<p local-id=3D"94256cb9-a22f-42ed-b851-edb2385e98ca">Notifications sent imm=
ediately after auto-cancellation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e91b8fe1-b462-420b-b55c-3c288b068e62">
<p local-id=3D"f4ee231a-62bb-448a-b779-9383487b9c6f">Email delivery handled=
 asynchronously</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"05097caf-8981-4c01-ab30-7cb3f9a634e4">
<p local-id=3D"c0f5ae5f-a98f-4537-91a0-bb531206d350"><strong>Reminder Syste=
m:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"58f69791-338d-451c-8774-23b739a8dc05">
<li local-id=3D"53536d40-c4d5-466f-9e79-05482694317f">
<p local-id=3D"d49fa064-4492-44da-aa1f-bd2b0e91853e">System sends reminder =
