s"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"694883e5-9852-4a5d-9f3e-69a496d6584d">
<p local-id=3D"e968f377-b81c-4e9b-b6a4-97aa48a931e7">Reminder content: Cour=
se details, pending approval status, deadline, link to approval screen</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c006806-9aa1-4722-b193-b0fbab9064a8">
<p local-id=3D"29f61a19-22e6-4370-a6eb-cb51e9f2a433"><strong>Exception Hand=
ling:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9d92cc24-edb3-49f8-8b9f-e13b2c232ba8">
