<hr local-id=3D"f2865824-cc2a-42f9-a281-f37e9cb432c6">
<h2 local-id=3D"9d070347-4942-4ffd-843a-a063e2c7ae23" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.5CourseEdit">8.5 Course Edit</h2>
<p local-id=3D"baf803e7-7f17-41d2-bdfa-f1d55e71dc9f"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS a Trainer, Lead Region, Head Channel, Admin, or Master Role user <br>
I NEED to edit course information <br>
SO THAT I can update course details based on my authorization level and cou=
rse status</p>
<p local-id=3D"5f8b3792-e3eb-488a-8417-5f005fd6187d"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"7bd39c86-f242-40a8-b5b7-e34c7bf8e02e">
<li local-id=3D"eb033aa6-ddee-4856-969d-02b35ce80a19">
<p local-id=3D"3b3b8541-f203-466e-86da-de894a10aae3"><strong>Edit Access Po=
ints:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ea8414cf-adfa-4a50-b888-61369480fbd8">
<li local-id=3D"decfd96e-dc39-4687-9b6f-4cab75bce3b7">
<p local-id=3D"49ae0685-e252-48a8-b893-1d70e48e2afc">Edit option available =
in Master Calendar (right-click on course =E2=86=92 "Edit" option)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"17980d31-4b0c-46cc-86cb-43013cf9cc90">
<p local-id=3D"468ee2ea-4d31-47ae-bbc8-ae7183e6e9e9">Edit button available =
