<h3 local-id=3D"22e95856-dd28-455a-a7e5-83dffba278f8" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.5.3Field-LevelRestrictions">8.5.3 Field-Level Restrictions</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3c9c99bf-14d6-4192-8c80-d9f4fe02b274"><strong>Admin Restrict=
ions (SHINE, APPROVED status):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"eeb3016d-4cbe-403d-9837-1c18e4d339b5">
<li local-id=3D"5295ce18-7ad1-4aca-99c2-40379e139f1b">
<p local-id=3D"9ff5115f-6db7-455b-b115-243b1117fa35">Admin can only edit MO=
F class code field</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88f979f1-9244-4f97-96e5-fae9d7b2eb7b">
<p local-id=3D"44fd36f6-36b6-4a8d-9dc6-e4b19939e2bd">All other fields block=
ed for Admin role</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d7009898-5ef8-4cc3-869d-9f9d76145038">
<p local-id=3D"dc6b76a7-dc4b-4377-8700-db2343eea5ec">MOF class code edit do=
es not require approval workflow</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"49c433b9-5e8b-444c-b527-ad15c9838454"><strong>All Other Auth=
orized Users:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"fbbdb9b5-9e9e-42fd-85a5-489813fbaeba">
<li local-id=3D"b5c7e938-ee45-4fb6-b694-a625abc813db">
<p local-id=3D"badb2b21-965d-4868-96cc-1ed3cc16aa22">Can edit all course fi=
elds (same as creation form - Section 8.1.1)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86cdea6d-169f-42ee-8785-c7c9a15c00f1">
<p local-id=3D"bcc36c2a-1954-48c8-a976-ec9df598c627">Field validation rules=
 same as creation form</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f93a83ce-8fae-4231-8961-5ea680ad96ba">
<p local-id=3D"ece755e9-d0df-433f-a515-2b5b55ddc1b4">All edits subject to a=
pproval workflow if applicable</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aff8d5d3-3fd1-4bc0-be37-21b7a93309ec"><strong>Exception Case=
s:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"dfa6974b-3852-423e-9629-c385233a8a21">
<li local-id=3D"7ac9c464-effb-4c41-a9f3-62e54887c99f">
<p local-id=3D"6f375d5e-29f3-4aa6-a032-a065c1917d6d"><strong>Master Role Ov=
erride:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"fefb2820-f57b-4326-b9b4-28620d2e43a4">
<li local-id=3D"9bf5e3b8-bfd3-4730-986c-0a987f075816">
<p local-id=3D"a4b071ad-e8dc-450a-a2a4-eced8d7ce4f9">Master Role can edit c=
ourses in ANY status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f3ac936-34b8-4b6d-bd33-aa29a749c6e7">
<p local-id=3D"97f1e3f2-a4ed-4163-9ed0-bcdf26fabba3">Bypasses all approval =
workflows</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4511c8e-420a-4ccd-9707-24135d943333">
<p local-id=3D"b4ed168b-f22b-4efb-88fd-bcd30a1f9cd0">Bypasses all status re=
strictions</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"f85115d9-296e-4cd9-9177-8ac755aa6729">
<p local-id=3D"871784a5-a074-45af-bbdd-1502cee0be5e"><strong>Trainer Restri=
ctions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7a7c35e4-70bf-42b5-b0f0-b41f5c56f9bd">
<li local-id=3D"0ddd893c-ef59-467d-b678-7809d1f2531a">
<p local-id=3D"2d389edf-a590-4369-a916-e3a385068269">Trainer (creator) can =
only edit when status is NEW (creator check required)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03f9817b-8ae1-4f9f-82df-3c39da4d827d">
<p local-id=3D"790a97e1-061c-4f9c-9b18-e0687e1dedd5">Trainer (primary) can =
only edit when status is REGISTERED (primary trainer check required)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"8cee0e45-d728-408b-ab85-8357b49e7ffd">
<p local-id=3D"97e94e4a-45ca-46df-99e8-f6f0671e4065">Cannot edit when statu=
s is APPROVED (SHINE) or IN_PROGRESS</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ae25c57-d1eb-4920-9029-42a10d922bb8">
<p local-id=3D"fc09b87a-19b4-47da-ab83-7676eb774af1"><strong>Admin Restrict=
ions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd5b569f-de47-4993-9d6a-b5757af3aeae">
<li local-id=3D"89ba4e55-6348-423a-bf95-7b03d5568634">
<p local-id=3D"2890b20d-dc75-461e-b3c2-b73e063cbe43">Admin can only edit MO=
F class code when course is SHINE type and status is APPROVED</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b7d9735c-b733-4e96-b194-dd0a0c64977b">
<p local-id=3D"b388fc72-941a-4cfd-8232-c50882c75ea4">Cannot edit any other =
fields in APPROVED status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f2dd28e-4762-46e7-bc5b-9e18c5ce8368">
<p local-id=3D"3ff625a7-094e-44b1-82c3-47394ec3b95e">Cannot edit courses in=
 other statuses</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"4b7d30c2-3b58-48f4-b9d9-55696e81ccdb">
<h2 local-id=3D"072955b6-2a11-481b-986b-917451e127e6" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.6CourseCancel">8.6 Course Cancel</h2>
<p local-id=3D"be2c30c1-591d-47a7-aebc-36baca886c23"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS a Trainer, Lead Region, Head Channel, or authorized user <br>
I NEED to cancel a course <br>
SO THAT I can prevent courses from running when circumstances change</p>
<p local-id=3D"77661307-668e-4838-8990-8cdab0bc970b"><strong>Business Use C=
ases:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1cf52b72-5e5e-4f55-bb3a-d9b16acf738c">
<li local-id=3D"fc064280-7a2e-4d2e-901d-33290f55b495">
<p local-id=3D"77fd761c-4451-417c-a92e-45465ac71322">Trainer requests cance=
llation due to scheduling conflicts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ea79ba8-3707-4cc6-a82b-e87f8624c36e">
<p local-id=3D"79125658-e671-42f9-b08e-6845e37a738e">Lead/Head cancels cour=
se due to low enrollment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7bec6c12-cfa5-4bc1-a15e-8b9fcfd154ae">
<p local-id=3D"01cd1e7c-ccd5-417a-be4a-febdf0a0a493">System tracks cancella=
tion requests and approval workflow</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c693c93a-7960-41f1-9520-d20070214add">
<p local-id=3D"c70f9e79-ad72-474f-9066-1a8e1b289f77">Cancelled courses are =
marked and removed from active schedules</p></li>
</ul>
