<p local-id=3D"29ebf942-4d38-46b2-8dd8-3e76376abc7b"><strong>Cancellation F=
low:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"863d8ee0-2b9f-4180-9ec2-b93970597db7">
<li local-id=3D"db8cad7a-0b51-4960-9b0b-6b6dcd0a4627">
<p local-id=3D"04053c84-c907-4553-b9e5-8e9c3de30360"><strong>Initiate Cance=
llation:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed8102d2-f197-4358-81c0-1acc26adfc1f">
<li local-id=3D"82ff8cfb-541e-469b-a7ff-ca7d211e1504">
<p local-id=3D"80ba45bd-7c3f-44ff-9dcb-fa880880a5da">User clicks "Cancel" b=
utton/option on a course</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c4d08c1-5d5e-4686-b8a1-ec67c984663f">
<p local-id=3D"f456ef1d-3573-4e3b-9dd4-f607da9edd4a">System validates user =
authorization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0047c5cc-b256-404c-a082-4964802f00dc">
