<p local-id=3D"cf0c1b1a-a79b-480a-90f3-7146a7546e50"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8a0c92c0-bcbd-47a8-9868-7e309e88a62d">
<li local-id=3D"2848c9f0-b35a-4897-8750-f6d3313199fd">
<p local-id=3D"7e468e70-b242-4498-8f3d-4559c6333041"><strong>Cancellation R=
eason Mandatory:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3ce0ce25-0d85-4fe1-981d-7381b95497bd">
<li local-id=3D"18f73b77-8495-4407-ba10-b47da1379404">
<p local-id=3D"aaae9a7f-db41-4e83-9398-be384345bc1b">Cancellation reason mu=
st be provided (cannot be empty)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"141bdbe0-2fd6-4f47-952a-617cde0b4c34">
<p local-id=3D"486f3210-7ff6-41ad-930c-d91792864729">Minimum length: 10 cha=
racters</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67406653-ff5a-4324-bc93-d0ce3ccf12f7">
<p local-id=3D"a3311b72-7883-4d9e-b691-ebe0703aa91f">Maximum length: 500 ch=
aracters</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"51c8db71-2bbb-45db-ba07-b7bac07f3025">
<p local-id=3D"91739908-35de-4eb0-abb0-52bc537a68ef">Reason is stored in Co=
urse History for audit trail</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"31db28dd-64ef-4db1-8449-02b065eceba5">
<p local-id=3D"903076df-bc2a-4bef-94a2-fe4b74edd041"><strong>Status Validat=
ion:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3986013e-a993-4891-82bc-406c32b5dd39">
<li local-id=3D"137680c4-7ef3-4bb1-87ad-33c5ccf0c051">
<p local-id=3D"b9dab08e-202f-4b8a-ba9d-fdf31da6f9fb">Cannot cancel if cours=
e status is already CANCEL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ddda5fff-3a43-44e9-ad7c-bf614151229f">
<p local-id=3D"fbae593f-abb3-46ec-9491-9205faa7929f">Cannot cancel if cours=
e status is FINISHED</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4455b49d-399d-42e5-8c10-08c8e563b213">
<p local-id=3D"7a7a80a3-a210-49b9-82e6-ead994634ca5">Cannot cancel if cours=
e status is DELETE</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e69967f4-070f-4fd7-9d0b-5b369da1ec6b">
<p local-id=3D"28fb2d79-03eb-485c-be0a-ff86cd442bdf">Can cancel from any ot=
her status (NEW, REGISTERED, APPROVED, IN_PROGRESS, WAITING_APPROVAL_EDIT)<=
/p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"66dc9ffd-3987-486e-bf7b-d22abc51b372">
<p local-id=3D"276d7fa1-faf4-4949-b7ad-196a34ff5bcf"><strong>Authorization =
Validation:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"50faca92-7fe5-481a-ad11-23a6324a3075">
<li local-id=3D"5adf2d86-4b2b-4a10-983e-88eac5d7dfad">
<p local-id=3D"ce080014-ed9c-47ef-97cf-bf501944ad7c">Trainer can only cance=
l courses where they are primary trainer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2d17de17-fd52-4ca2-86f0-e281632af233">
<p local-id=3D"a5f6628c-d89f-492e-8ee2-06e0fa04ae37">Lead Region can only c=
ancel courses in their channel AND region</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33e8b50d-c6ac-41a2-8d2b-ce25361de0b5">
<p local-id=3D"1d46ad83-8478-4d39-a10d-2be7d4817776">Head Channel can cance=
l courses in their channel</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2c6e060-72ab-430b-8cff-460444c8428c">
<p local-id=3D"cd52f034-6dd1-4e89-91ea-61354f950c0e">Master Role can cancel=
 any course</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"eaef6d54-4572-4e9c-85c7-dd532bb7d643">
<p local-id=3D"f60c080e-210e-49b6-99a8-956be09a1aab"><strong>Auto-Approval =
Rules:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a164cc4a-e0f7-479b-8de2-8d250969b6bc">
<li local-id=3D"bc9d4756-c08c-4454-88c2-bef2287b22c4">
<p local-id=3D"7fec0331-15ef-4c86-99c6-a1ed01c2f32c"><strong>Users with </s=
trong><code>self_approval</code> permission: Cancellation is automatically =
approved (no approval workflow)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46bf5750-2411-4e14-a8bd-3815c69b07ee">
<p local-id=3D"f5a6f9af-8237-4719-86ac-5f517058ebc7"><strong>Default assign=
ment</strong>: Head Channel role has <code>self_approval</code> permission =
by default</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f8c3e8b-5cb0-404e-8cad-ccb82ba576e2">
<p local-id=3D"0ca4c4c2-07dc-45fd-b6c4-0e0a9d71d444"><strong>Configurable</=
strong>: Root Admin can assign <code>self_approval</code> permission to any=
 role or individual user</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dff2c416-0d7e-4283-8459-09982dee17f4">
<p local-id=3D"54ea531b-b28a-4189-9490-122ca90c0c49"><strong>Permission che=
ck</strong>: System checks for <code>self_approval</code> permission before=
 routing to approval workflow</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"42266087-c21b-4a80-9984-927b1ee2b272">
<p local-id=3D"9ce59e81-13fe-499e-8ba7-fb706418be17"><strong>Master Role Ov=
erride:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"dbf64b1e-1c56-4f1b-bcb0-14e587ae739d">
<li local-id=3D"d5b3192f-7eb9-4639-81bc-a951255cf8cf">
<p local-id=3D"17a74024-6e09-48d0-91a3-f214e4fa92fd">Master Role can cancel=
 any course without approval</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"60035bc6-6887-49fb-987c-e960e6ef595e">
<p local-id=3D"3aab938b-a5c7-46e7-94fc-72d5ed7eaafa">Bypasses all approval =
workflows</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3141feaa-fc2e-4eaa-a104-6b016d26986f">
<p local-id=3D"68ef21ec-1383-4570-93ff-fc8565957648">Bypasses all status re=
strictions (except CANCEL, FINISHED, DELETE)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"78421f8e-d78e-4385-906f-61b0ebc2c382" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.6.2CancelApprovalWorkflow">8.6.2 Cancel Approval Workflow</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7b9b2259-38c5-4c75-b1d0-2e27d030bf0c"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS A Head Channel or Lead Region <br>
I NEED to approve or reject course cancellation requests <br>
SO THAT I can control which courses are cancelled and ensure proper resourc=
e management</p>
