<p local-id=3D"8ab6780c-b2eb-4b18-b2db-b2867f266762">All approval/rejection=
 actions recorded in Course History</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16807881-16ee-496c-ad5e-08459d531589">
<p local-id=3D"0638f3aa-7771-41e8-9396-783de653b6d5">Includes: User, Role, =
Timestamp, Reason (for rejection)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"457588a7-d2d9-4c20-ac75-3956dd72a5c8">
<p local-id=3D"ad95e8ec-c61d-4930-a5b9-8a2f42a24b4e">Cannot be deleted or m=
odified</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"bd1f0af4-8e41-409f-8b6c-bae35b930e48">
<h2 local-id=3D"a69fdb02-6763-4bd1-9a0a-22ba4e60c6c8" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.7CourseDelete">8.7 Course Delete</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d9cfeb09-dee8-4b8d-a359-0a086a615048"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS a Trainer, Lead Region, Head Channel, or authorized user <br>
I NEED to delete a course <br>
SO THAT I can remove courses that are no longer needed or were created in e=
rror</p>
<p local-id=3D"c18945c5-460e-41ed-8ad2-b0d4194e6847"><strong>Business Use C=
ases:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"48b5002a-5557-4fd6-b8d4-31e8546e4f75">
<li local-id=3D"b4f5e39b-dda5-4b8c-8834-d8a7b8b3ce9a">
<p local-id=3D"98320475-2030-470f-a8a2-162ade954767">Delete course created =
in error</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3418a8c2-e0c3-4bf1-9587-e41b3cd3f054">
<p local-id=3D"dec9d4d9-4f1b-43c8-aa60-b434c060102c">Remove duplicate cours=
es</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2b390dc-0f12-464e-9ebb-515931e0aae7">
<p local-id=3D"fc0e7fea-ced2-47ac-8d7b-9952390ba8a9">Clean up test or cance=
lled courses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19aecc6c-bdd2-4e61-be63-9cf0f0ffea8e">
<p local-id=3D"b36715db-4ce4-47e3-b69e-6ce40c8fbeaf">System tracks deletion=
 for audit purposes</p></li>
</ul>
