<p local-id=3D"14544548-14e2-4999-8cfd-5f55ecf88705"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"5eabab68-9300-4867-a8cb-84bae7bb08aa">
<li local-id=3D"44d7501d-a6db-4593-968f-ff8d0a16bd41">
<p local-id=3D"cfb0e12d-b5c6-466e-8fa5-766238725c0a"><strong>Status-Based R=
estrictions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1cf20730-9e12-40aa-b22b-13c3a394f588">
<li local-id=3D"1fb0076b-3d47-43d3-901d-351ab83be88b">
<p local-id=3D"dd60a99b-3f57-4633-9b4b-6b6d341173d6">Courses in APPROVED, I=
N_PROGRESS, or FINISHED status cannot be deleted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19746e88-9f58-46e7-95a3-97c5e322250b">
<p local-id=3D"373d423f-50b2-40a5-a16f-affcb9fb62f8">Use cancellation funct=
ion instead for active courses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f52e1c7c-6495-4183-af4d-7cdd6e759daa">
<p local-id=3D"2a6aa942-d3ff-494c-9ac3-e582aa06d9e2">Only NEW, REGISTERED, =
or CANCEL courses can be deleted</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"62d1f33f-79d6-4b06-9289-415b668fccf2">
<p local-id=3D"484fecea-f730-4a5a-b43a-bae889501312"><strong>Participant Ch=
eck:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"54026f57-1477-45fc-904e-131e2d3ffc5c">
<li local-id=3D"f5ae025e-b64e-4c59-a14d-40d3949757e9">
<p local-id=3D"8aedee09-5ea9-41de-bd22-69c88a2b3a0f">Courses with participa=
nts should not be deleted (use cancel instead)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77b88873-cf39-45bd-a14b-6e0a345a629c">
<p local-id=3D"99a961f2-bf49-4998-b0e8-068342a3a8bf">System warns if course=
 has participants before deletion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ca36de2e-d05d-4ec0-9d40-95d0a388def0">
<p local-id=3D"8c960f60-14fa-4cb1-8e05-4c16307fa2ad">Master Role can overri=
de participant check</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"218ea687-2ac1-45d6-bc1e-bbde940d0727">
<p local-id=3D"d971dc5c-876b-46d1-822b-c9111529da8f"><strong>Creator Check =
(for Trainer):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"44b10d35-d7bc-47bd-badb-9d93ce5a73b8">
<li local-id=3D"a1b5589a-8818-4e58-8117-5acb4904b2d6">
<p local-id=3D"f1672d8e-38c8-41a6-913a-02b10c1b5925">Trainer can only delet=
e courses they created</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afc56ac6-6efa-4269-b8b9-280a0d2cf321">
<p local-id=3D"87558bd7-1635-4f9d-ac74-537fa80b1188">System validates creat=
or ID matches current user</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"043aa0aa-dd76-49c4-9e5a-68d6af5ce8d1">
<p local-id=3D"669c5067-9176-409c-b55a-0f6bffb1aa25"><strong>Master Role Ov=
erride:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"c77f2958-5930-4714-bc26-d5bd9e1f52e5">
<li local-id=3D"c2a20001-b048-46fe-8000-4200ecc440c4">
<p local-id=3D"2ce2094f-a9d0-40cd-8375-f53ad8898810">Master Role can delete=
 any course in any status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ebcb13c-1c75-4471-ba1c-0854c21ef6cd">
<p local-id=3D"4d111f4e-4031-4a4c-a7d7-c819821a6464">Bypasses all restricti=
ons</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3331c96-5ae3-4b46-ac35-17360825adbe">
<p local-id=3D"894b6d20-f350-4819-bac9-1d739da2d486">Use with caution for a=
udit purposes</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"ce756d8d-b349-483d-8ff9-4b0bd903fe3a" id=3D"CourseActions-8=
.7.2SoftDeletevsHardDelete">8.7.2 Soft Delete vs Hard Delete</h3>
<p local-id=3D"098fdb10-045a-4d15-a1c0-ba763fe6a6e3"><strong>Soft Delete (D=
efault Behavior):</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"5779122b-18fd-4719-9926-94e85071b238"><strong>Purpose:</stro=
ng> <br>
Retain course data for audit and reporting purposes while removing it from =
active views.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5a8dc5c6-cf9c-480c-954d-0a29d8c2c126"><strong>Implementation=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"88969663-0456-4cf0-a950-2ff1772a0f86">
<li local-id=3D"b03c0648-f2ad-4318-b948-e1288f7b1d21">
<p local-id=3D"2b1b8f04-cdf7-4fd7-b997-34df3a4afcd0">Course status set to D=
ELETE</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e9a8667-374a-46ff-91b7-ebcd02a0a176">
<p local-id=3D"caecf25c-9909-4ef7-94c0-55b945d733f7">Course hidden from all=
 lists and dropdowns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21a84a4b-6016-4745-bb68-00d507fcfde1">
<p local-id=3D"70c33f98-9638-459d-8348-ffcc9541454f">Course data retained i=
n database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73923519-11bc-47f0-9eb6-63f3b35979f2">
<p local-id=3D"595381e5-893d-4908-80f7-e1bb2335f553">Course history preserv=
ed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea02666f-5877-4a3f-a33f-753ec9d9e1fc">
<p local-id=3D"8d22f650-090f-4df6-8389-424e3ec5ad03">Can be restored by Mas=
ter Role (future enhancement)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9d86fe61-2d67-4f9c-b970-752cd2b9583b"><strong>Soft Delete Pr=
ocess:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ad26094d-0a71-47cc-a0db-adc59a45bd4a">
<li local-id=3D"b090f138-1eaa-4748-877b-00c337e45204">
<p local-id=3D"4782e9a2-090e-46ae-8d8f-b0df60d6bec5"><strong>Update Course =
Record:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"323dac06-a1c2-48d6-8d6b-470c0d676d62">
<li local-id=3D"91b9f3e0-86bb-4730-a025-5b75dff66352">
<p local-id=3D"dabdf243-3c5d-4e7d-8a9e-38f38188335b">Status: Current Status=
 =E2=86=92 DELETE</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b948dd86-1dd1-4c16-aad4-b40472163ece">
<p local-id=3D"f5d70593-c55c-47c5-ac7e-f1c3c4357791">Deleted By: User name =
and role</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ea9cb38-d2c6-4b03-9f01-3442a87de0fa">
<p local-id=3D"f8879487-d99e-4d40-8c73-1c87f9df88c8">Deleted Date: Current =
timestamp</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ad2ebb0-7ac9-4f95-8322-350b6d5dac50">
<p local-id=3D"14bf31f5-db1b-4d01-b0a9-97ef96937014">Deletion Reason: Optio=
nal (can be captured in confirmation dialog)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b57de6f-ff05-4c7a-b21f-efd27974c228">
<p local-id=3D"06b575cd-dd43-4773-9d0e-80f612c696c8"><strong>Update Course =
History:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"902b707e-92ad-4f32-a471-8d6715622b0f">
<li local-id=3D"a31ecb8e-357d-43a2-ad8a-d5a3a899ebe3">
<p local-id=3D"2b6c3523-ea98-4403-bad5-d2b460978f3d">Action: "Course Delete=
d"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7391bdc0-fb2f-4400-987e-2ed3a7a4828c">
<p local-id=3D"8133aff8-2539-479b-968a-6548f52bcf74">User: Deleter name and=
 role</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"338dc6eb-fcb1-4fc1-a6d1-876234631ea4">
<p local-id=3D"0dec1767-9da9-4e61-aef6-949e58cd5d85">Timestamp: Current dat=
e/time</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"44dd6140-944d-4a37-a1b7-1f3c0b422693">
<p local-id=3D"46a0ac39-7b05-4471-9f49-98f347be2ae8"><strong>Update Status =
Timeline:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2fcb7d3b-bacc-480a-b00f-14f04eb8432a">
<li local-id=3D"daed97b7-b840-474d-b50a-5591c422dd29">
<p local-id=3D"fe144b7d-bcb6-4db4-9e88-86cfcd87a0ef">Add DELETE milestone</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b56c881-1648-4199-b8b1-c06f2703af26">
<p local-id=3D"725ea914-a2de-4434-a1e7-8640838bc5e2">Record deleter name an=
d timestamp</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bed8818-92ca-4a3a-9d35-b4850baedbe5">
<p local-id=3D"7e119ddf-1590-4fe4-9391-ac1f3f1bff59"><strong>Hide from View=
s:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d035e99c-5000-4a1a-aa96-f2debf84cd18">
<li local-id=3D"71888c9c-1bfb-4455-99f4-636a6ccef6a0">
<p local-id=3D"a7b1607a-7a3f-45a0-a5c1-51c8233f28b5">Remove from Course Lis=
t (unless filter includes deleted)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21ad5ba0-cb39-4e94-8b1b-9c20ecd61af9">
<p local-id=3D"553c9f01-58de-4fbe-8504-31890f92f3d2">Remove from Master Cal=
endar</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a491c5ff-22b0-4faa-acf7-7eaa09ece925">
<p local-id=3D"3aedfde5-8295-4bda-9e6a-354bc8dc2c1b">Remove from PIC Calend=
ar</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"26c47270-0075-46c7-9ac9-279c9419b144">
<p local-id=3D"63a05d00-7b74-4e23-b23d-f5340e4c9003">Remove from all dropdo=
wns and selections</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"47fb3a40-e023-456a-b077-4e5f3a4ead8a">
<p local-id=3D"38be9aea-c42b-49d9-93c6-2bbde7ed9dec"><strong>Send Notificat=
ions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4cc13839-d9cb-4ce1-b317-e121da324122">
<li local-id=3D"d471ecec-bf69-4a62-a8ab-3fffdefc4a53">
<p local-id=3D"bdd8f8ba-6729-47da-b397-1abc1c92f29b"><strong>To Course Crea=
tor:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5d26a5d5-df4f-4acb-9e90-a6b518e4fd1e">
<li local-id=3D"2d2d27ad-ca45-4a70-8c33-988dac55a76d">
<p local-id=3D"e35a48c9-7a25-44de-9c05-4ff8ca2a6ad8">Subject: "[LMS] Course=
 Deleted: [Course Code]"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c975a8e-9166-4fbb-b462-3a6d4e662e7b">
<p local-id=3D"facdae51-3dc8-447b-905b-ca15d81e5d7f">Content: Course detail=
s, deletion date</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1f21a41-1d2b-4a33-adc0-7661d6ae11aa">
<p local-id=3D"9a1e0909-6acd-4d66-a725-244c6497e788"><strong>To Primary Tra=
iner (if different from creator):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"23598b3e-83cc-4ef4-b70a-dfb07e01f37b">
<li local-id=3D"92ff8c9c-9694-4b68-9300-09516db7141d">
